How will banks work?
- Players can open a bank account for 500 Coins
- They can input 1,000+ coins in their bank account for 1 Week (1% Interest/Week), 4 Weeks (2% Interest/Week) or 12 Weeks (3% Interest/Week)
- They CANNOT take out coins for that number of days
- Once the period ends, they will get coins with interest

